Package: ADS8192
Title: ADS 8192 Expression Heatmap Builder
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Abby", "Kaur", , "abhineet.kaur@stjude.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to generate genes x samples heatmap for data visualization on SummarizedExperiment objects. Selects for most variable genes, performs k-means clustering, generates heatmap, and exports matrix to TSV files. Created for ABDS 8192 Course Homework 1.
